WESTERN SOUTH ATLANTIC.
URUGUAY.
1. SEISMIC SURVEY 21 MAR BY M/V RAMFORM VANGUARD TOWING 12
   7000 METER LONG CABLES ALONG TRACKLINES BETWEEN:
   A. 35-39.88S 053-04.45W AND 35-28.40S 052-52.88W.
   B. 35-18.05S 052-42.02W AND 35-07.05S 052-31.07W.
   NINE MILE BERTH REQUESTED.
2. CANCEL HYDROLANT 773/14.
3. CANCEL THIS MSG 22 MAR 14.
